Simplified and Asynchronous Security Context Interfaces for the Generic Security Services Application Programming InterfaceAbstract This Internet-Draft proposes extensions to the Generic Security Services Application Programming Interface (GSS-API) for replacing the exiting GSS_Init_sec_context() and GSS_Accept_sec_context() functions with simplified forms that also support asynchrony.
